  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will give emergency help to kids &amp; families, fire victims in Attika, Greece. We will create Help Stations to cover the Fire Victims with food, clothes, psychological support, and medicines. At the areas with no electricity, we will provide energy banks and internet sticks. We cover Mati, Kinetta and the kids Camp.of Rafina.  H.U.G. POINTS will provide in person  psychological support in this dark period, as well as, nutrition, tools and essentials on a daily basis.</narrative>
  </description>
